            <tr>
                <td valign="top"><p><strong>Defense of Discipline </strong></p>
                    <p>a. Position of Authority<br />
                        b. Enforcing Discipline</p>
                    <p><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; letter-spacing:normal; orphans:2; text-align:start; text-indent:0px; text-transform:none; white-space:normal; widows:2; word-spacing:0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial; display:inline !important; float:none; font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">Under tort law a person with&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">recognized authority</strong><span style="font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">&nbsp;(schoolteacher, bus driver, airplane pilot, policeman, parent, etc.) is privileged to&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">act reasonably</strong><span style="font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">&nbsp;given the circumstances in a manner that&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">otherwise might constitute</strong><span style="font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">&nbsp;a&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">battery</strong><span style="font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">&nbsp;or false imprisonment.</span> </p>
                    <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td valign="top"><p><strong>Defense of Authority of Law </strong></p>
                    <p>a. Reasonable Force<br />
                        b. Prevent or Stop Felony or Disturbance of Peace<br />
                        c. In Presence of Them</p>
                    <p><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; letter-spacing:normal; orphans:2; text-align:start; text-indent:0px; text-transform:none; white-space:normal; widows:2; word-spacing:0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial; display:inline !important; float:none; font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">Under tort law a person is privileged to act&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">reasonably</strong><span style="font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">&nbsp;to prevent or&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">stop a FELONY</strong><span style="font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">&nbsp;or DISTURBANCE OF THE PEACE from being committed in their presence.</span> </p>
                    <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td valign="top"><p><strong>Defense of Consent </strong></p>
                    <p>a. Fully informed consent<br />
                        b. Person with Legal Capacity<br />
                        c. not for battery</p>
                    <p><span style="font-variant-ligatures:normal; font-variant-caps:normal; letter-spacing:normal; orphans:2; text-align:start; text-indent:0px; text-transform:none; white-space:normal; widows:2; word-spacing:0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px; background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style:initial; text-decoration-color:initial; display:inline !important; float:none; font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">Under tort law&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">FULLY INFORMED CONSENT</strong><span style="font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">&nbsp;from a person with legal capacity is a&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">defense</strong><span style="font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">&nbsp;to most intentional torts, but is&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">not</strong><span style="font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">&nbsp;a defense to a&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: verdana; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;">battery</strong><span style="font-family:verdana; font-size:12px; color:rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style:normal; font-weight:400; ">&nbsp;that causes foreseeable great bodily injury.</span> </p>
                    <p>&nbsp;</p></td>
